<section class="home-shop-section">
	<div class="home-shop-container">
		<!-- Materials We Use Section -->
		<div class="home-shop-section-header home-shop-section-header-spaced">
			<p class="home-shop-section-subtitle">THE LOCKER ROOM</p>
			<h2 class="home-shop-section-title">MATERIALS WE USE</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="ts-spotlight-inner-centered">
			<div class="ts-spotlight-content">
				<a href="/products" class="ts-spotlight-position">Premium Materials Collection</a>
				<div class="ts-spotlight-meta">
					<span>6-Layer Plywood</span> | <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="melamineLinkBtn" class="material-link">Melamine Finishes</a> | <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="woodGrainLinkBtn" class="material-link">Wood Grain</a> | <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="phenolicLinkBtn" class="material-link">Phenolic Options</a> | <a href="/colors/essential-wood-pdf.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="material-link">Essential Wood PDF</a> | <span>ENF Certified</span> | <span>Fully Customizable</span>
				</div>
				<p class="ts-spotlight-bio">Built with premium 6-layer melamine-faced plywood featuring superior moisture resistance, termite protection, and fire-rated construction. Our proprietary layering process creates a core that's 40% stronger than standard plywood while meeting or exceeding all safety codes. Choose from an extensive range of melamine and laminate finishes including authentic woodgrain patterns, designer solid colors, and textured finishes. Each finish delivers exceptional durability and easy maintenance while maintaining the aesthetic appeal of natural wood. Also available in phenolic plastic for extreme durability in high-moisture locker room environments with 100% waterproof construction—perfect for pool areas, ice rinks, or any facility requiring maximum moisture resistance. All materials are ENF certified (zero harmful chemicals), water-resistant, and anti-fungal. Available in any dimension with your choice of finish, color, and hardware. Custom colors available upon request.</p>
				<div class="materials-buttons-container">
					<button id="viewAllColorsBtn" class="ts-btn ts-btn-filled">View All Colors</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

